Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. - Michael Henry Schwerner Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system otherwise known as the "3rd Street Bridge" as the "Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. - Michael Henry Schwerner Memorial Bridge" connecting Mount Vernon, county of Westchester with the town of Pelham, county of Westchester.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Martin Luther King Jr. - Michael Henry Schwerner Memorial Bridge"
